txt.en: I figured we'd eventually be sunk by the Eye, or maybe the north-men...
Raghârik raises deadly cyclones....
TBD
\qDNT - BUMPER CHECK\q
Vast wing-beats herald Raghârik's arrival upon the aerie!
Raghârik's wings raise a great storm upon the Aerie!
That'll be quite far enough!
Bad enough that great ape slaughtered me and my crew.
Can't say as I saw that one coming.
Now ye've come to pick through our bones as well?
Nay... I think it'd be best if ye were joining my crew instead!
Are ye bloody serious?
Aye. Know thy enemy, right?
Though I suppose it's a bit late for that. Innit...
... I knew I shoulda gutted you when we was still alive.
You can tell on account of he hadn't got a tail and all.
How long do you reckon we've been down here?
Can't say rightly. Didn't seem much point to keeping track to be honest...
Y'know, signing on with a pirate crew weren't what I imagined...
But bein 'et by a ruddy great monkey?
T'was an ape.
Eh? What now?
He weren't a monkey - he were an ape.
